As your TypeScript projects grow in complexity, so does the need to fine-tune your tooling to match your teamŌĆÖs workflow, performance requirements, and architectural standards. TypeScriptŌĆÖs extensibility allows developers to go beyond standard configurations and craft custom solutions that streamline development, enforce consistency, and even automate critical parts of the build pipeline.

