- Enforcement of naming conventions or structure

### Example: GitHub Actions Pipeline for TypeScript

```yaml
# .github/workflows/typescript.yml
name: TypeScript CI

on: [push, pull_request]

jobs:
  type-check:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
