Write a snapshot test:

```typescript
import { describe, it, expect } from 'vitest';
import { createUserProfile } from './profile';

describe('createUserProfile', () => {
  it('generates a valid user profile', () => {
    const result = createUserProfile({ id: 'user-123', name: 'Alice' });
    expect(result).toMatchSnapshot();
  });
});
```

The first run creates a snapshot file (`__snapshots__/profile.test.ts.snap`):

```snap
