exports[`createUserProfile generates a valid user profile 1`] = `
{
  "id": "user-123",
  "name": "Alice",
  "settings": {
    "theme": "light",
    "notifications": true,
    "language": "en",
  },
  "lastLogin": Any<String>,
}
`;
```

> ­¤öŹ **Example**: You modify `createUserProfile` to exclude `lastLogin`. The test fails:
> ```
